---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { SITE } from "../../config";
import { t } from "../../i18n";

const lang = "en";
const socials = Object.entries(SITE.socials).filter(([_, url]) => url);
---

<BaseLayout title={t(lang, "about.title")} lang={lang}>
  <section class="about">
    <img src={SITE.author.avatar} alt={SITE.author.name[lang]} class="avatar" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
    <h1>{SITE.author.name[lang]}</h1>

    <div class="prose about-content">
      <p>😎 The Adventures of Eric from Texas — Confessions of a Code Wrangler</p>
      <p>Hey there! I'm Eric, a globally nomadic coder who was made in Shanghai, upgraded in Canada, and currently running in the USA. 🎭</p>
      <h2>🚀 Life Changelog</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>v1.0 (1977): Released in Shanghai. Plenty of childhood bugs, but shipped with a built-in explorer spirit.</li>
        <li>v2.0 (2006): Migrated to Canada, successfully acquired the "Maple Leaf Shield," and switched to a new server. 🍁</li>
        <li>v3.0 (Now): Wandered into USA, currently customizing my life script and trying to become a Solopreneur — with the goal of building a passive income empire through code! 💰💡</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>🎮 Career Path — From Coder to Entrepreneur to Free Spirit</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Once started a game company, dreaming of creating the next <em>Mario</em>. Ended up stepping on so many landmines that life turned into a Soulslike game 👾.</li>
        <li>Plenty of experience as a big-tech worker bee. Witnessed the magic of capitalism, but ultimately decided to escape the 9-to-5 and become my own boss.</li>
        <li>Now going all in on being a Solopreneur. The goal: "Earn my own money, spend my own money, and never read the boss's mood again!" 😎</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>🏆 Life Principles</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Code must run, wallets must grow, and people must be free!</li>
        <li>If it can be automated, never do it manually! (Including making money)</li>
        <li>Life is like a startup — you'll never know if you'll hit it big unless you try!</li>
      </ol>
      <p>🚀 <strong>The new journey has just begun. Welcome aboard — let's witness the rise of a Solopreneur together!</strong> 💡💰</p>
    </div>

    {socials.length > 0 && (
      <div class="social-links">
        {socials.map(([name, url]) => (
          <a href={url} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">{name}</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    )}
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 0;
  }

  .avatar {
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border: 3px solid var(--primary);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-content {
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .social-link {
    padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-transform: capitalize;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .social-link:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white;
  }
</style>
